<b><u>EDUCATION</u></b>
<p>
Curative Health Services has a very strong commitment to education and
training.  We believe our concentrated focus on education is a cornerstone
to the success of our Wound Management Program.  A major component of this
educational process is an internet-based training system known as the
<a href="./login.htm"> "Curative Professional Courseware"</a>.  This system is used around the country
in the Wound Management Program by Curative-affiliated professionals. 
